OL,3,CThe reason why Reform UK chose to
OL,4,Claunch its 'contract' in Wales
OL,6,FNigel Farage has unveiled Reform UK's
OL,7,Fmanifesto, which the party has dubbed
OL,8,Fas a "contract" with voters.
OL,10,FSpeaking today (17 June) in Merthyr
OL,11,FTydfil, Mr Farage set out Reform UK's
OL,12,Fpledges to voters.
OL,14,FIt is not the first time that Mr
OL,15,FFarage has come to this part of Wales.
OL,16,FDuring the 2019 General Election, he
OL,17,Ftook part in a Brexit Party rally at
OL,18,FTrago Mills.
