OL,3,CThe reason why Reform UK chose to
OL,4,Claunch its 'contract' in Wales
OL,6,FHowever, this time round, leading the
OL,7,FReform UK party, he said he wants to
OL,8,Flaunch "a crusade to defend British
OL,9,Fvalues".
OL,11,FBut why choose Wales as its launch
OL,12,Flocation?
OL,14,FSpeaking at the Reform UK manifesto
OL,15,Flaunch, Mr Farage described "a broken
OL,16,FBritain" where nothing "actually works
OL,17,Fanymore".
