OL,3,CThe reason why Reform UK chose to
OL,4,Claunch its 'contract' in Wales
OL,6,FHe said: "We've chosen to launch our
OL,7,Fcontract in Wales, which seems highly,
OL,8,Fhighly appropriate. After all, Labour
OL,9,Fhave been in power here since 1997.
OL,11,F"So, perhaps there are some lessons
OL,12,Fthat we can learn from 25 years of
OL,13,FLabour Government in Wales - at
OL,14,Fperhaps what we may have to look
OL,15,Fforward to in just a few weeks' time
OL,16,Fwhen Sir Keir Starmer becomes our
OL,17,Fprime minister."
