OL,3,CThe reason why Reform UK chose to
OL,4,Claunch its 'contract' in Wales
OL,6,FHe continued: "In Wales, taxes are
OL,7,Fhigher, yes they are. Council Tax is
OL,8,Fhigher, on average about #500 per
OL,9,Fmedium property than it is in England."
OL,11,FAccording to each respective
OL,12,Fgovernment's website, the council tax
OL,13,Ffor a Band D house in Wales is #2,024
OL,14,Fwhereas it is #2,171 in England.
