OL,3,CThe reason why Reform UK chose to
OL,4,Claunch its 'contract' in Wales
OL,6,FHe continued: "So the people in Wales
OL,7,Fpay more taxes, and spending per
OL,8,Fcapita is higher in Wales than it is
OL,9,Fin England. There's more money being
OL,10,Fspent on you on public services than
OL,11,Fthere is on the other side of the
OL,12,Fbridge.
OL,14,F"Perhaps that wouldn't matter if it
OL,15,Fled to better delivery".
OL,17,FMr Farage proceeded to discuss NHS
OL,18,Fwaiting times differing between Wales
OL,19,Fand England, claiming people in Wales
OL,20,Fhave to wait 50% longer than they
OL,21,Fwould across the border.
