OL,3,CThe reason why Reform UK chose to
OL,4,Claunch its 'contract' in Wales
OL,6,FHe also added that Wales has fallen
OL,7,Ffurther behind England in education
OL,8,Fand that the Labour government here
OL,9,F"reduced your freedom", through
OL,10,Fmeasures such as the controversial
OL,11,F20mph speed limit law - which saw
OL,12,FWales become the first nation in the
OL,13,FUK to adopt 20mph as the default speed
OL,14,Flimit on restricted roads.
OL,16,FIn a statement ahead of the launch, Mr
OL,17,FFarage said that Reform UK chose
OL,18,FMerthyr Tydfil as the launch location
OL,19,Fas it "shows everyone exactly what
OL,20,Fhappens to a country when Labour is in
OL,21,Fcharge".
