OL,3,CThe reason why Reform UK chose to
OL,4,Claunch its 'contract' in Wales
OL,6,F"It's no wonder that all of Farage's
OL,7,Fparty were turfed out of the Welsh
OL,8,FParliament at the last election."
OL,10,FMr Farage also levelled criticism at
OL,11,Fthe Conservatives in the Senedd,
OL,12,Fcalling the party "feeble", saying
OL,13,Fthey hadn't achieved anything as the
OL,14,Fopposition to Labour in Wales.
OL,16,FResponding to those claims, Andrew RT
OL,17,FDavies MS, Leader of the Welsh
OL,18,FConservatives, said: "The Welsh
OL,19,FConservatives have been robust in
OL,20,Fholding Labour to account on
OL,21,Fimmigration in the Senedd.
