OL,3,CThe reason why Reform UK chose to
OL,4,Claunch its 'contract' in Wales
OL,6,F"When Reform's predecessor party UKIP
OL,7,Fgot seven Members to the Senedd in
OL,8,F2016, they quickly descended into
OL,9,Finfighting and defections,
OL,10,Fdisenfranchising hundreds of thousands
OL,11,Fof voters and giving Labour an easy
OL,12,Fride.
OL,14,F"The Welsh Conservatives will continue
OL,15,Fto scrutinise the Labour Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment and call for them to
OL,17,Feliminate dangerous pull-factors which
OL,18,Fbenefit people smugglers."
