OL,3,CThe reason why Reform UK chose to
OL,4,Claunch its 'contract' in Wales
OL,6,FA Plaid Cymru spokesperson said: "For
OL,7,FNigel Farage, Wales is nothing but a
OL,8,Fprop to boost his own ego. He has sold
OL,9,Flies to people in postindustrial areas
OL,10,Fin the past and will do so again
OL,11,Ftomorrow.
OL,13,F"Reform will blame all of Wales' ills
OL,14,Fon immigration, but what areas like
OL,15,FMerthyr Tydfil need is investment and
OL,16,Fjobs, not Nigel Farage's divisive
OL,17,Fagenda."
